karofaOa, 
inf. n. karofaOapN; 
and tkrfO↓; (like krvO and tkrvO, Ḳ, which are said to be changed from the former; TA;) It (a collection of clouds) became large in quantity, and confused, and heaped up. (Ḳ.)

